sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'; import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography'; import { Button, Card } from '@material-ui/core'; import Link from 'next/link'; import PropTypes from 'prop-types'; import { useStyles } from './car-list-item.styles'; export function CarListItem({ _id, brand, model, price, year, photo }) { const classes = useStyles(); return ( {brand} {model} Price: {`$ ${price}`} Year: {year} ); } CarListItem.propTypes = { _id: PropTypes.string.isRequired, brand: PropTypes.string.isRequired, model: PropTypes.string.isRequired, price: PropTypes.number.isRequired, year: PropTypes.number.isRequired, photo: PropTypes.string.isRequired, };
